(That's where you're wrong KSL. There is no main moderator. Power is 
spilt evenly among the council. Nobody does anything without everyone 
going for it. What you are saying is that you are basically in charge 
of the RPG, and Yanshosh and JP and whoever else is on the council 
are just your minions making smaller decisions. If you are going to 
be saying that you have the power and if you are going to keep 
nagging to everyone about little rules, than I would be the first to 
place my vote to get you off the council. I'm sure there are others 
who agree with me. If there are not, than I will be quiet. But I'm 
not going to just shut up and let you take control.)

Vulois

Vulois' face lit up with a smile.

"I would do anything to get back to Cybertron. It's better than 
living here." He looked to Cybershark, "Are you up to it?"
______________________________________________________________________
Starscream

Starscream found Inferno and another bot talking. He decided to stay 
above them until Drillbit arrived. No sense in going two on one. 
Maybe they could take them both back.
